ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T03:04:11.000Z","msg":"都幾肯定上一輩仲多人唔識佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0590217260ae8c4f438318f3c0a14892f2f03121","tid":160503,"uid":48618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T03:04:48.000Z","msg":"利申 96年 因為王家衛而諗識<br />\n<br />\n最愛天堂與地獄"},{"pid":"dfd698775f8ac5705d2fc30d29cf4a94ba809b9f","tid":160503,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T03:09:16.000Z","msg":"酒徒"},{"pid":"f29ebdf7846c3da63e972354f483e9e24a0186d1","tid":160503,"uid":1291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T03:15:08.000Z","msg":"劉已傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd4703266e0de53e19ee9bf4957a07152a9c57ea","tid":160503,"uid":32442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T03:16:25.000Z","msg":"打飛機都算啦 搵個咁出名既黎打醜唔醜啊<br />\n停止呢種老屎忽文化啦好嗎<br />\n直接講後生係原罪啦"},{"pid":"5d969973e403d213d2f9b932885b72c1abe2a096","tid":160503,"uid":52360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T03:18:41.000Z","msg":"95後，打錯了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cde1dc7ae9fa14eedfde9f3363aeb491edac507e","tid":160503,"uid":38261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T03:32:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>懶係有文化打撚哂飛機咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小學推介好書都有佢啦，屌你老味係佢寫得叻，唔喺睇佢本書果個叻呀臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咩誤會？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 問有冇人識又打飛機<br />\n乜都冇講過又句句粗口咁撻過嚟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你呢啲蠢人都睇過，當然代表唔係睇過佢本書個個叻喇</blockquote><br />\n慘 潛左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係話樓豬咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8d467699b56bc0b77ee9662b7dc627806d921c0","tid":160503,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T03:35:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打飛機都算啦 搵個咁出名既黎打醜唔醜啊<br />\n停止呢種老屎忽文化啦好嗎<br />\n直接講後生係原罪啦</blockquote><br />\n香港既年輕人仲有幾多個識梁朝偉?"},{"pid":"81fe1c6af305a67672567017b7b80191ee11496f","tid":160503,"uid":28726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T03:36:21.000Z","msg":"有無人都有去舊年個《對倒》主題電車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d95cfd53dffdf3e3b2c08e0576b4aaca1cbfc721","tid":160503,"uid":29247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T03:41:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/18/023102_45ff2a31ea8aa6c388238e00b052e101.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F18%2F023102_45ff2a31ea8aa6c388238e00b052e101.jpg&h=d8d49a1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我書架<br />\n中學嘅時候老師推薦過<br />\n本身係鍾意睇電影 專登睇完酒徒先睇王家衛嘅花樣同2046</blockquote><br />\n掉左本彭志銘去啦"},{"pid":"0357a4d694c45a1792687d4bada508acc6b4f9b7","tid":160503,"uid":390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T03:57:41.000Z","msg":"以前中學有介紹過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家出街行書局成日都留意到佢啲書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1504739cf1ffbcf99acffc9d0d378d2aead64b6","tid":160503,"uid":683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T03:59:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔好話識佢咁高難度<br />\n齋個鬯字都唔知有幾多個人係知點讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個真，